sentence: Should I take EECS 281 and EECS 370 at the same time ?
sentence-with-vars: Should I take department0 number0 and department0 number1 at the same time ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE ( ( COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 280 ) OR ( COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 370 ) ) AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ;
